::Epyon::

"Ok. Good," he says to Prowl.
He then gets the message from Alpha Dolphy.
"I'll go and help."
He turns to Wizard. 
"Please get everyone ready for the City project. And start taking apart
the ship if you get to that point. I'll be back."
He makes his way to the hatch, and gets out. He swims to the surface.
"Beast mode."
He transformes to his dragon mode, and heads towards Angel prime's
location.
